@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName 微软雅黑

' --- 定义输入层 ---
rectangle "输入层" as input_group {
  card "验证场景剖面 SP\n(来自研究内容二)" as ScenarioProfile #FFD2B4
  card "状态机模型 M\n(来自研究内容一)" as StateMachineModel #B4D8FF
  card "形式化性质 P\n(来自研究内容二)" as FormalProperty #D2B4FF
}

' --- 定义LLM智能辅助层 ---
package "大语言模型 (LLM) 智能辅助" as llm_group {
  usecase "1. 场景实例化\n与路径生成" as PathGen #MintCream
  usecase "2. 缺陷诊断\n与根因分析" as Diagnosis #MintCream
  usecase "3. 结果解释\n与报告生成" as Interpretation #MintCream
}

' --- 定义核心验证框架 ---
rectangle "时间状态机验证框架" as engine_group {
  card "符号执行\n与区域图分析" as SymbolicEngine #FFB4DA
  card "性质检测器\n(模型检测器)" as Checker #FFB4DA
  card "反例生成器" as CexGenerator #FFB4DA
}

' --- 定义数据流 ---
card "执行轨迹/状态空间" as Trace #LightGrey

' --- 定义输出层 ---
  card "验证结果报告" as VerificationReport #B4FFDA
  note right
**验证结果报告**
• 性质满足情况
• 缺陷列表与严重等级
• 反例执行轨迹
• 根因定位建议
  end note
  card "缺陷定位信息" as DefectInfo #B4FFDA


' --- 连接数据流 ---
' 输入层 -> LLM辅助
ScenarioProfile --> PathGen
StateMachineModel --> PathGen
FormalProperty --> Checker

' LLM辅助 -> 验证引擎
PathGen --> SymbolicEngine
SymbolicEngine --> Trace
Trace --> Checker

' 验证引擎 -> LLM辅助
Checker --> CexGenerator
CexGenerator --> DefectInfo
DefectInfo --> Diagnosis
Diagnosis --> Interpretation

' LLM辅助 -> 输出层
Interpretation --> VerificationReport

' 内部关联
PathGen ..> Interpretation : 提供上下文
Checker ..> Diagnosis : 触发分析
Trace ..> Diagnosis : 提供分析依据
@enduml